derline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer System (Maintenance and Troubleshooting Guide)<\/span><\/a><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><a href=\"https:\/\/www.agilent.com\/cs\/library\/usermanuals\/Public\/G2938-90007_Inst-Safet_EN.pdf\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">Agilent 2100 Bioanalyzer (Installation and Safety Guide)<\/span><\/a><\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><a href=\"https:\/\/emea.support.illumina.com\/bulletins\/2016\/11\/converting-ngl-to-nm-when-calculating-dsdna-library-concentration-.html\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">Converting ng\/\u00b5l to nM when calculating dsDNA library concentration<\/span><\/a><span style = \":;\"><\/span><\/div><div class = \"text-block\">If using Illumina Library Prep protocols, refer to the following <\/div><div class = \"text-block\"><a href=\"https:\/\/emea.support.illumina.com\/bulletins\/2016\/05\/library-quantification-and-quality-control-quick-reference-guide.html\" style = \"text-decoration:underline;color:blue;cursor:pointer;\"><span style = \":;\">Library quantification and quality control quick reference guide<\/span><\/a><\/div><\/div>"}},{"id":1054725,"guid":"643DBAE859734BB38C8032254DA1208C","order_id":2,"type_id":26,"title":"notes","source":{"id":0,"parent_id":0,"uri":"","title":"","body":"<div class = \"text-blocks\"><div class = \"text-block\">Ensure that the mean fragment sizes of the replicates do not vary by >5% of each other. <\/div><\/div>","created_on":0,"changed_on":0,"creator":{"name":" ","affiliation":null,"affiliations":[],"username":"","note":null,"link":null,"image":{"source":"","placeholder":""},"badges":[],"verified":0,"is_verified_user":false,"research_interests":null,"blocked_by_you":false,"blocked_you":false,"hide_following":false},"comments":[]}}],"cases":[],"data":null,"html":null,"section":null,"section_color":"#94EBFF","section_du